ferential geometry into living systems can assist in the\ngrowth of comparative neuromechanics, allowing comparison of self-deformation\ndynamics across taxa and providing hypotheses for function at lower levels of\norganization.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 26 Jun 2019 22:50:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 22 Feb 2022 03:14:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-23"}
