ects (\"Kronian\" stars and non-periodical dips in dusty\nlightcurves). Additionally, the typical transit timing variations (TTV) induced\nby the interaction of a ploonet with its planet are computed. We find that\npresent and future photometric surveys' capabilities can detect these effects\nand distinguish them from those produced by other nearby planetary encounters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 00:35:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2019 20:14:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Dec 2019 16:58:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-25"}
