 technique against using the complete list\nof OWASP high-level security requirements. The (statistically significant)\nresults indicate that using the reading technique has a positive impact (with\nvery large effect size) on the performance of inspectors in terms of\neffectiveness and efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 04:41:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-28"}
