al dynamics can have in shaping large-scale functional\nbrain states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 12:00:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 9 Jul 2020 12:10:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-10"}
