The methodology presented is illustrated on the\nconstruction of the symmetry-adapted representations both of the potential\nenergy function of ethane and of the rotation, torsion and vibration basis set\nfunctions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 15:32:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-28"}
