st three order smaller than uncertainties in time\nmeasurement of the recently observed GW/GRB signals and thus calls for\nimprovement if $\\Delta t_{\\mathrm{p}v}$ is to be used to further constrain the\nGW velocity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 09:18:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-25"}
