 results have shown the meaningfulness of the\nproposed modularity, revealing the effects of different combinations of the\nresolution and inter-layer coupling functions. This work also represents a\nstarting point for the development of new optimization methods for community\ndetection in multilayer networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 27 Jun 2019 10:49:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-15"}
